" Annoying
noremap  <F1> <Nop>
inoremap <F1> <Nop>

" Clear search on Esc
nnoremap <silent> <Esc> :nohlsearch<CR>

" Quick save
noremap <C-S> :wa<CR>

" Ctrl-Backspace and Alt-Backspace like everywhere else
inoremap <Esc><Backspace> <C-W>
cnoremap <Esc><Backspace> <C-W>
inoremap <C-H> <C-W>
cnoremap <C-H> <C-W>
